  <brief_title>A Phase Ⅰa Study of Remimazolam Tosylate in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Placebo- and Midazolam-Controlled, Phase Ia, Single Ascending-Dose Study Evaluating the Safety, Pharmacokinetics, and Pharmacodynamics of Remimazolam Tosylate</official_title>
  <sponsors>
